                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Spirit of the Whale."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " You smuggled stolen dwarven spirits in the body of a dead whale being pulled behind a fishing boat. When you delivered the goods, the corpse suddenly exploded, sending whale meat and whiskey bottles for half a mile."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
