                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "The Recruit."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " You enlisted in another nation's navy for the purpose of smuggling stolen jewels to a distant port. You attained a minor rank before disappearing from the navy and making your way here."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
          },
          {
            "type": "element",
