                    "children": [
                      {
                        "type": "text",
                        "text": "Playing Both Sides."
                      }
                    ]
                  },
                  {
                    "type": "text",
                    "text": " You once smuggled crates of crossbow bolts and bundles of arrows, each destined for an opposing side in a regional war, at the same time. The buyers arrived within moments of each other but did not discover your trickery."
                  }
                ]
              }
            ]
